                    <h2>Overview</h2>
                    <p>A fortune 250 IT company requested DXC to develop an application in collaboraton with a third-party firm. In my role as the UX Delivery Lead, I was tasked with facilitating design direction by outlining specifics of the UI, formalizing execution of the front-end, and facilitating communication with all stakeholders.<a href="ux_process.html" class=""> Learn more about my UX process</a></p>
