                <div class="col-lg-8 mb-0 mb-lg-2">
                    <blockquote class="bqspecial bqstext p-4 text-left font-weight-normal my-6 font-size-5"><h2>Goal</h2>The goal was to deliver an MVP for client beta testing in 14 weeks. A side goal was to show our client and the design firm that we are strong in development and can partner together seamlessly for future projects.</blockquote>

                    <h2>Process</h2>
                    <h4>Discovery and COVID</h4>
                    <p>In-person workshops were quickly adjusted to virtual due to COVID. The initial launch of the opportunity consisted of 2 weeks of virtual workshops with our client, the design firm, and DXC to determine build strategy. I represented the needs of the development team from a front-end perspective and initiated deep-dive sessions based on further requirements gathering needs. Virtual working due to COVID brought about challenges in initial discovery where tools like Mural, Teams, Abstract, WebEx, Box, Slack were essential.</p>
                    </div>

