                    <h4>Growth opportunity to flex my development skills</h4>
                    <p>Due to being short staffed initially for front-end development, I stepped up to assist the team to ensure timely delivery. I coded based on styling tweaks to better align with the design mock-ups. In order to do this, I quickly completed development coursework to get up to speed on Carbon Framework and REACT. By completing this essential coursework, I formed a better understanding of Carbon Framework components and could clearly identify advantages and constraints due to client requested customizations.</p>
